OL,3,CGreater Manchester police chief
OL,4,Cpraises Home Secretary's plans for
OL,5,Coverhaul
OL,7,FReacting to Shabana Mahmood's
OL,8,Fproposals, which include slashing the
OL,9,Fnumber of police forces and creating a
OL,10,Fnew National Police Service (NPS) to
OL,11,Ftackle major crimes, Sir Stephen
OL,12,FWatson said: "I think the Home
OL,13,FSecretary has properly taken the bull
OL,14,Fby the horns.
OL,16,F"These are bold announcements in
OL,17,Frespect of the reform which to
OL,18,Fpolicing is literally decades in the
OL,19,Fcoming."
