OL,3,CGreater Manchester police chief
OL,4,Cpraises Home Secretary's plans for
OL,5,Coverhaul
OL,7,FHe said the current system, with 43
OL,8,Fforces accountable to 43 people, was
OL,9,F"not efficient or effective".
OL,11,F"I applaud the Home Secretary's
OL,12,Fcourage in bringing forward what are
OL,13,Fbold proposals.
OL,15,F"I don't think it's before time, and I
OL,16,Fthink that when we talk in the
OL,17,Flanguage of once-in-a-lifetime,
OL,18,Fgenerational, transformational change
OL,19,Fin policing, that is precisely what
OL,20,Fthis is, and that, for me, is very
OL,21,Fexciting, and certainly it is due."
