OL,3,CGreater Manchester police chief
OL,4,Cpraises Home Secretary's plans for
OL,5,Coverhaul
OL,7,FHe said he was "reasonably relaxed"
OL,8,Fabout plans which would see the Home
OL,9,FSecretary given the ability to sack
OL,10,Fchief constables.
OL,12,F"The Home Secretary is accountable for
OL,13,Fmuch of what happens in policing's
OL,14,Fname across the country, and if their
OL,15,Fdetermination is that they need to
OL,16,Ftake powers in very, very rare
OL,17,Fcircumstances to dispense with the
OL,18,Fservices of a chief constable, then
OL,19,Fthat will be a decision of our
OL,20,Fdemocratically elected politicians,"
OL,21,Fhe said.
