OL,3,CGreater Manchester police chief
OL,4,Cpraises Home Secretary's plans for
OL,5,Coverhaul
OL,7,FSir Stephen described an emphasis on
OL,8,Flocal policing areas as "really
OL,9,Fimportant" but developments such as
OL,10,Fthe advent of cyber crime and a more
OL,11,Fmobile society meant structures needed
OL,12,Fto change.
OL,14,FHe said: "There is something genuinely
OL,15,Fold-fashioned about policing services
OL,16,Fthat reflect a world that is no longer
OL,17,Fas it might have been 50 or 60 years
OL,18,Fago and that's literally what we're
OL,19,Ftalking about in terms of the current
OL,20,Fpolicing construct."
